column3: Please squash these into a single commit.\n
I have squashed the three into one commit.\n
Thanks @MarcoFalke. I have dropped the changes from src/univalue/\* here and I have submitted them as a PR to @jgarzik's main univalue repo.\n
@isle2983 Can you rebase this so it can be merged?\n

rebased and conflicts resolved in four files

src/policy/policy.cpp - The conflict was with date being bumped to '2016' by a prior commit on the same line as this pull's edit.

src/policy/policy.h - same as with policy.cpp

src/test/bctest.py - The conflict was with a new 'The Bitcoin Core developers' copyright holder was added in the adjacent line to my edit where the comma was removed afte
univalue is a subtree. You'd need to change it upstream.\n
